  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498580/extras/534a6b655dd3fe4e2b2f49cd55d31f87.webp?t=1660054976\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><strong>A Narrative FPS game that starts when several years ago your company discovered a machine which appears to open doorways that go to not only different places but also peoples nightmares.</strong><br><br><strong>Badges :</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498580/extras/c7d3ac9c02fc277e52c7f74b33f89170.avif?t=1660054976\" width=80 height=80 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498580/extras/2d627266ea5f56989dda2361f2e78e04.avif?t=1660054976\" width=80 height=80 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498580/extras/24b7f74b6119b9af254154cc68afd26d.avif?t=1660054976\" width=80 height=80 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498580/extras/8be2fc730aac5eb9ec665d5811b060e2.avif?t=1660054976\" width=80 height=80 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498580/extras/3333c2517f2f8d6fd6f1d34be11b7a46.avif?t=1660054976\" width=80 height=80 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498580/extras/188dfa936281456fe3e0f91ec9d0b3d4.avif?t=1660054976\" width=80 height=80 /></span>  <br><br>You are hired to explore each different environment or nightmare and discover the reason to why this machine exists in the first place.  <br><br>Encounter new and strange environments, creature